        <abstract> 
<p>Has read CD’s queries in the <hi rend="italic">Field</hi> regarding the markings of dun-coloured horses. JS has for some years been working on and observing the occurrence of ass-like striped markings in horses and wonders whether CD received any response to his queries.</p> 
